title: Episode 161 w/ DJ Jazzy Jeff
itunes:title: Episode 161 w/ DJ Jazzy Jeff
description:
N.O.R.E & DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. On this episode the champs sit down and chop it up with Philly Legend Dj Jazzy Jeff. They talk about his early roots in Philly, the Fresh Prince, Will Smith and much more.Later in the episode are also joined by special guests A-Trak and DJ Craze for more DJ talk.
